    "code": "import flopscope as fnp\n\nfnp.array_equal([1, 2], [1, 2])\n\nfnp.array_equal(fnp.array([1, 2]), fnp.array([1, 2]))\n\nfnp.array_equal([1, 2], [1, 2, 3])\n\nfnp.array_equal([1, 2], [1, 4])\n\na = fnp.array([1, fnp.nan])\n\nfnp.array_equal(a, a)\n\nfnp.array_equal(a, a, equal_nan=True)\n\na = fnp.array([1 + 1j])\n\nb = a.copy()\n\na.real = fnp.nan\n\nb.imag = fnp.nan\n\nfnp.array_equal(a, b, equal_nan=True)",
